{"tid":1788215,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"《是咁的，我間酒店迫我HOUSE-USE訓停屍間DKLM》","createTime":"2019-12-18T13:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T11:09:53.000Z","uid":125607,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"881838442084182e7297a7b567e170463355eebb","tid":1788215,"uid":125607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"利申返先：小弟做五星M酒店，係operation同事。無論落幾大粒狗屎，打既風有幾撚大都好，我地都係on call 36小時。Office同事就開開心等收工等放假，我就要諗點樣仆返公司‥不過做酒店有樣野唔知叫好定唔好，阿頭會叫我地HOUSE-USE，即係訓酒店房，話唔使驚返唔到工喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都知依排好興全民三罷呀；和你塞呀；黎明行動架啦，阿頭就驚死冇人返工，強迫我地HOUSE-USE喎！大佬，我自己一支公同埋我隻愛犬住，我唔返一晚呀愛犬掛住我架嘛！唔返一晚都算，你叫我連續訓3晚？邊撚個幫我睇住我愛犬呀？訓3晚就係驚我返唔到工？我講到明我行路都一定行到返黎公司咁好未。我屌佢老味，佢話有得訓就好訓啦遲啲冇得你訓添呀冇床俾你訓呀咁喎？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都算鳩數，重點係您老味五星大檔，訓唔到尊貴既酒店房都算。係呀！我冇房訓架！OCC得3成都唔撚俾房啲同事住，刻薄到世界盡頭。我住果啲係大ballroom，然後鋪啲吹氣床係地下，唔講我以為我訓停屍間呀屌。同啲扯到好撚大‥‥鼻寒既麻甩佬訓，真係攞我命3000！我訓都訓唔到，J又打唔到，我第日邊有精神返工呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呻完，請問有冇巴絲同我一樣被迫HOUSE-USE？我聽隔離酒店巴打講，叫你HOUSE-USE唔訓但第日返唔到工既話，會扣鳩佢ANNUAL假‥到底是咪CLS？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ff0a251959e2a25247b3e5dbfee1e5e7165ba3","tid":1788215,"uid":182098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"真心痴線<br />\n好刻薄囉 我都聽過人地話同事用既房唔會執 一床輪流瞓<br />\n翻用condom咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心啲膠層啦 一間正正常常房都唔施捨下俾員工"},{"pid":"70cd664c409416f46b7dd7a213c6de77a22e5d4d","tid":1788215,"uid":180745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"下 咁都得<br />\n放工番屋企人身自由黎<br />\nD高層咁仆街既<br />\n唔好理佢照番屋企啦<br />\n反正佢夜晚又check唔到你有冇走既<br />\n<br />\n我係絲都覺得冇得打J好慘 屌"},{"pid":"0b90ea6f8e2484408cc57bc3b667355bf6415ac7","tid":1788215,"uid":46624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"我呀爸都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢做酒店餐廳<br />\n之前預計第二日有8號10號就會開始叫聽日要返工嘅人返咗酒店先<br />\n返唔到扣annual / 曠工處理<br />\n個日放緊假都要返咗去瞓到第二日<br />\n3罷唔洗講<br />\n好多日都叫爸爸係酒店瞓<br />\n姐係你要你間酒店營運<br />\n我唔撚洗見我老豆嘅概念"},{"pid":"9280119cae51005094331cfb5f1011e5f263f8a2","tid":1788215,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"我都係大檔<br />\n不過自己揀留唔留<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有得一個人一間房call 埋條女嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要瞓停屍間即刻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13203d922909fe88a46cd44770ea8c96364b49c","tid":1788215,"uid":118276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"邊間甘pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7640b34eea5f7289f6aeeeb2b6c8ab5ba367c6","tid":1788215,"uid":21611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"個排成日都houseuse<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5907569bac6f1856953611103aa68b2fc16cb9","tid":1788215,"uid":12586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"開名喇<br />\n平時occupancy 高就話姐，依家咁都唔撚俾房？<br />\n公司大撚哂呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d4c57b62962fbb1e53fb5e3d26ae87d2ea6a56","tid":1788215,"uid":54007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:08:52.000Z","msg":"九龍區R 字頭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5baaa4829ba92495e69456c387d2c4b90da9c6","tid":1788215,"uid":70055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:12:26.000Z","msg":"仆佢個街完全唔當自己員工係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明日做夜做最辛苦就係前線員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經濟好嗰陣做到仆街都算<br />\n經濟唔好嗰陣mgnt 一話cut cost 就卸落前線staff度, 搞到啲staff 做到死咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未計打風就被逼 house use 啲衰嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店前線幾時先可以唔被高層當condom咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係已經有人組左工會喇咩<br />\n樓主揾工會幫拖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3776787c48865c493ab2b15b8c826984d4a4e7f","tid":1788215,"uid":70055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"推到有工會撚見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14220b3eb8d623a780f3a22763f206ba5f69b66e","tid":1788215,"uid":125607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9280119cae51005094331cfb5f1011e5f263f8a2","tid":1788215,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"我都係大檔<br />\n不過自己揀留唔留<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有得一個人一間房call 埋條女嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要瞓停屍間即刻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"有得一人一間咁好 我見啲frd最好個個都係三個人訓一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb8c7731385ec5ecfade6ef84bf8ec9154ba3bb","tid":1788215,"uid":182098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14220b3eb8d623a780f3a22763f206ba5f69b66e","tid":1788215,"uid":125607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9280119cae51005094331cfb5f1011e5f263